Kafka commands:

Start zookeper:

bin/zookeeper-server-start.sh config/zookeeper.properties

start kafka:
bin/kafka-server-start.sh config/server.properties

list topics:
bin/kafka-topics.sh --list --bootstrap-server localhost:9092


create topic:
bin/kafka-topics.sh --create --topic test-topic --bootstrap-server localhost:9092 --partitions 1 --replication-factor 1

create topic with retention:
bin/kafka-topics.sh --create --topic test-topic --bootstrap-server localhost:9092 --partitions 1 --replication-factor 1 --config retention.ms=604800000

Prevent Future Deletes: 
    • Edit config/server.properties (~2 min, Week 2 tweak): 
        ◦ Add: delete.topic.enable=false—stops manual deletes (restart Kafka after).
Run consumer:
bin/kafka-console-consumer.sh --topic test-topic --from-beginning --bootstrap-server localhost:9092

Run producer:
bin/kafka-console-producer.sh --topic test-topic --bootstrap-server localhost:9092

add more partitions to producer:
bin/kafka-topics.sh --alter --topic test-topic --bootstrap-server localhost:9092 --partitions 10